Holistic health may seem like an "alternative" health view; however, I believe that it's the most important way to view our health. 

Instead of putting a bandaid on our problems, and wondering why we keep needing a new, bigger one, holistic health focuses on healing the underlying problem first.

So what is holistic health? 

Holistic health is made up of 5 aspects of health. Focusing on healing all 5 of them, even if symptoms are only in one.

